scene.message:
Mark: A 'Persona', huh?{nl}
Like that'd ever show you{nl}
your future self.{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey, Brown...{nl}
is your head feeling{nl}
a little too warm?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Heh heh.{nl}
Don't go knockin' it,{nl}
man!{waitkey}{clearbox}Okay, seein' the future{nl}
is goin' a bit far, but it's{nl}
a real paranormal deal!{waitkey}{nl}
I'll even bet you on it, Mark!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Alright, a bet?{nl}
Loser treats everyone to{nl}
all-you-can-eat at{nl}
Peace Diner!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Tch!{nl}
Same as always.{nl}
What a bunch of{nl}
party poopers.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey.{nl}
Which side are you betting on?{nl}
Mine, obviously, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Geez, you too?{nl}
Every last one of you{nl}
is out of their mind.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Pff heh heh heh...{nl}
I'll make ya cry!{nl}
Alright, let's get started!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Um, let's see...{nl}
Persona, oh Persona,{nl}
please come to us~{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Alright!{nl}
Persona, oh Persona,{nl}
please come on out!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Man, seriously...{nl}
why do I have to do{nl}
something this stupid...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Yeah, yeah, fine.{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Persona, Persona,{nl}
come on out, whatever.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Now then...{nl}
Persona,{nl}
Persona,{waitkey}{nl}
please come forth...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: H-hey, Brown!{nl}
This makes Ayase{nl}
look like an idiot!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: See, look.{nl}
Nothing happened at all.{nl}
Heh heh, I win.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Phew...{nl}
feel better now?{nl}
Now go fetch the{nl}
teacher already.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: W-wait, hold on!{nl}
Just one more time! C'mon!{nl}
It's 'cause Mark joined in!{waitkey}{nl}
Put some spirit into it!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Oh, you little...{nl}
You sure don't know{nl}
when to quit, do ya.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Ha ha... s-see?{nl}
Just like I told you, right?{nl}
Bit different from{nl}
before, though...{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Inaba Masao{nl}
A.K.A. Mark. The wayward{nl}
son of Inaba Cleaners.{nl}
The impulsive type.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Nanjo Kei{nl}
A.K.A. Nanjo-kun. Heir to{nl}
the Nanjo conglomerate.{nl}
A staunch rationalist.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Mayuzumi Yukino.{nl}
A.K.A. Yukino.{nl}
The big-sister of the school,{nl}
trusted by everyone.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Ayase Yuka. A.K.A. Ayase.{nl}
A free-spirited trendy girl{nl}
and total troublemaker.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Kirishima Eriko. A.K.A. Elly.{nl}
A returnee young lady;{nl}
an intellectual beauty.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}
